Number of listed shares (Common          : 3,003,750,000
Stock)(shares)
Number of paid-up Stocks  (Common        : 3,003,750,000
Stock)(shares)
Par value (baht per share)               : 1.00
Paid-up capital (baht)                   : 3,003,750,000.00
IPO shares (shares)                      : 603,750,000
IPO's shares are consisted of            : Additional shares offered to public 
totaling 506,750,000 shares.
The share of existing shareholders offered to public totaling 97,000,000 shares.
Allocated to                             : Public totaling 600,750,000 shares.
The directors, managements and/or employees of company or subsidiaries (ESOP) 
totaling 3,000,000 shares.
IPO price (baht)                         : 25.00
IPO offering date                        : From 01-Oct-2018 to 10-Oct-2018
Business description                     :
Manufactures and sells consumer products which core products include (1) energy 
drinks, sold under the brand M-150 and Lipo etc., sports drinks and
ready-to-drink coffee and (2) personal care products, sold under the brand Babi
Mild and Twelve Plus. The Company also provides products manufacturing,
packaging and distributing services.
Remark                                   :
IPO shares were offered to investors and ESOP on October 1-4, 2018 and 
institutional investors on October 8-10, 2018. Please see the Information
Memorandum of OSP through PDF File.
